## Build

Prerequisites:
- `python3`
- `ca65`
- `ld65`

Main commands:

```sh
make rom
make validate
make smoke
```

Recommended clean rebuild:

```sh
make clean && make validate
```

## Emulator Workflow

Primary emulator target:
- Mesen 2 on macOS

What to verify first in emulator:
- title screen is stable
- `Start` enters gameplay
- player can move in all directions
- room transitions work correctly
- sword and enemy collisions behave as expected

See also:
- [docs/test-matrix.md](/Users/johnbrady/projects/NES-dungeon-crawler/docs/test-matrix.md)

## Documentation Conventions

- [docs/PROJECT_LEDGER.md](/Users/johnbrady/projects/NES-dungeon-crawler/docs/PROJECT_LEDGER.md) is the append-only project history and status file.
- New progress should be added there as new dated entries, not by rewriting older entries.
- [docs/REHYDRATION_PROMPT.md](/Users/johnbrady/projects/NES-dungeon-crawler/docs/REHYDRATION_PROMPT.md) is the handoff/bootstrap prompt for a new Codex session.

## Notes

- This repo is still in active development.
- `main` should reflect merged, buildable work.
